Frequently Asked Questions

What's your typical turnaround time?

Most orders are completed within 5-7 business days. Rush orders (48-72 hours) are available for an additional fee. Larger orders may require additional time.

Do you have minimum order quantities?

No minimum! We're happy to embroider a single item or thousands. However, larger quantities do get better per-piece pricing.

What file formats do you accept for artwork?

We accept most common formats including JPG, PNG, PDF, AI, EPS, and SVG. Vector files (AI, EPS, SVG) provide the best results for embroidery.

Can you match specific brand colors?

Yes! We have access to hundreds of thread colors and can match most brand colors. We'll send thread samples for approval before production if needed.
